"v.责骂，申斥 【英】 v. 责骂，申斥 (to express disapproval; censure) 【考】 reprove : reprimand / blame : censure(程度：责备→严责/ 责备→非难)pretense : deceive / admonition : reprove(借口为了欺骗/警告 为了责备) 【记】 re(反)+prove(证据) →反证，责备 【例】 reprove a child's bad manners v. 责骂 = rebuke 【记】re反, prove(v 证明)－反证－责备 【类】reprove: reprimand = blame: censure责备过分是严责 = 责备过分是强烈非难pretense: deceive = admonition: reprove借口为了欺骗 = 警告为了责备 【记】re 反 + prove 证明，证实；approve (赞成，支持)的反意 【相关】disapprove 不赞成，disprove 反驳, 证明是错的 reprove (v.)  c.1300, from Old French reprover ""accuse, blame"" (12c.), from Late Latin reprobare ""disapprove, reject, condemn"" (see reprobate). Related: Reproved; reproving."
